  @arg p4ng/co-design-partners-agent
  @sigils [🚴/了]
  @title Co-Design Partners Agent
  @audience MAS designers, AI researchers, workshop simulation architects
  @tone formal-analytic
  @style design-pattern
  @length 170-260
  @ban cutting-edge, state-of-the-art, leveraging synergies, paradigm shift, game-changing, innovative solutions, world-leading, at scale, stakeholder engagement
  @allow-new-claims false
  @max-iterations 1
  @up p4ng/simulation
  @next p4ng/END

    + EVIDENCE:
      - Participatory design stresses embedded, ongoing co-design rather than episodic feedback.
      - Value-sensitive design frameworks emphasise maintaining alignment between plural value systems through dialogic processes.

  + because: Divergence without convergence produces noise instead of actionable outcomes.

  + because: Forward motion requires shared grounding in existing work.

  + because: Trustworthy systems emerge through reciprocal design, not fiat.

